<hr>
<h2 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Overview">Over=
view</h2>
<p>The IAM PR Automation system is a Terraform-managed AWS solution that au=
tomatically validates IAM policy changes in GitHub Enterprise pull requests=
. The system operates in three distinct workflow paths:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Production Workflow</strong>: Real-time validation of open PRs =
from production IAM repositories (10 IDC repos)</li>
<li><strong>Test Workflow</strong>: Real-time validation of open PRs from t=
he test/POC repository for system testing</li>
<li><strong>Regression Testing Workflow</strong>: Historical PR validation =
for measuring automation accuracy</li>
</ol>
<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-KeyCapabilitie=
s">Key Capabilities</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Automated PR Discovery</strong>: Polls GitHub Enterprise every =
3 minutes for open PRs</li>
<li><strong>Parallel Validation</strong>: Runs security, compliance, and IA=
M boundary checks simultaneously</li>
<li><strong>Real-time Notifications</strong>: Sends results to MS Teams cha=
nnels</li>
<li><strong>Regression Testing</strong>: Validates automation accuracy agai=
nst historical human decisions</li>
<li><strong>Comprehensive Logging</strong>: Full audit trail in CloudWatch =
and DynamoDB</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-DataFlowDiagra=
ms">Data Flow Diagrams</h2>
