<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-ComponentOverv=
iew">Component Overview</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
<thead>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Component</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Type</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Purpose</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Trigger</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>PR Poller</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Lambda</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Discovers open PRs from GitHub Enterprise</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">EventBridge (every 3 min)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>Step Function Trigger</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Lambda</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Starts validation workflow</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">DynamoDB Stream (INSERT)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>Security Scan</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Lambda</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Validates IAM policy security</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Step Function</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>Compliance Check</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Lambda</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Validates IAM policy compliance</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Step Function</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>IAM Boundary Checker</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Lambda</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Validates IAM boundary policies</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Step Function</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>Final Status Checker</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Lambda</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Determines overall PASS/FAIL/ERROR</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Step Function</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>Teams Notifier</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Lambda</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Sends notifications to Teams</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">DynamoDB Stream (MODIFY)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>Historical PR Fetcher</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Lambda</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Fetches historical PRs for testing</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Manual/PR-triggered</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><strong>Regression Summary</strong></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Lambda</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Aggregates regression test results</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Final Status Checker</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-WorkflowTypes"=
>Workflow Types</h2>
<p>The system supports three distinct workflow types:</p>
<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-1.ProductionPR=
Workflow">1. Production PR Workflow</h3>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Validate new PRs from production IAM repositor=
ies</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: PR Poller discovers open PR<br><strong>Table</=
strong>: <code>github-open-prs-{env}</code><br><strong>Step Function</stron=
g>: <code>process-iam-pr-stepfunction</code><br><strong>Teams Channel</stro=
ng>: IAM-PR-Automation<br><strong>Duration</strong>: ~10-15 seconds (after =
PR detection)</p>
<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-2.TestPRWorkfl=
ow">2. Test PR Workflow</h3>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Validate PRs from test repository (POC)</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: PR Poller discovers open PR<br><strong>Table</=
strong>: <code>github-open-prs-{env}</code><br><strong>Step Function</stron=
g>: <code>process-iam-pr-stepfunction</code><br><strong>Teams Channel</stro=
ng>: IAM-PR-Automation-Test<br><strong>Duration</strong>: ~10-15 seconds (a=
fter PR detection)</p>
<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-3.RegressionTe=
stingWorkflow">3. Regression Testing Workflow</h3>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Validate automation accuracy using historical =
PRs</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: Manual invocation or PR with <code>[REGRESSION=
-TEST]</code> tag<br><strong>Table</strong>: <code>github-prs-regression-te=
st-{env}</code><br><strong>Step Function</strong>: <code>process-iam-pr-reg=
ression-stepfunction</code><br><strong>Teams Channel</strong>: IAM-PR-Autom=
ation-Regression<br><strong>Duration</strong>: ~20-30 minutes (full test cy=
cle)</p>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Infrastructure=
Components">Infrastructure Components</h2>
<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-DynamoDBTables=
">DynamoDB Tables</h3>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-ProductionTabl=
e:github-open-prs-{env}">Production Table: <code>github-open-prs-{env}</cod=
e></h4>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Stores production PR data and execution tracki=
ng</p>
<p><strong>Key Structure</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Partition Key</strong>: <code>repo_pr</code> (String) - Format:=
 <code>{org}/{repo}#{pr_number}</code></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Key Attributes</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>repo_pr</code>: Unique identifier (e.g., "Centralized-IAM-Account=
s/idc-gts-roles-prod#250")</li>
<li><code>repo</code>: Repository name</li>
<li><code>pr_number</code>: PR number</li>
<li><code>title</code>: PR title</li>
<li><code>author</code>: PR author</li>
<li><code>execution_status</code>: RUNNING | COMPLETED | FAILED</li>
<li><code>execution_id</code>: Step Function execution ID</li>
<li><code>security_scan_endstatus</code>: PASSED | FAILED | ERROR</li>
<li><code>compliance_check_endstatus</code>: PASSED | FAILED | ERROR</li>
<li><code>iam_boundary_check_endstatus</code>: PASSED | FAILED | ERROR</li>
<li><code>final_status</code>: PASSED | FAILED | ERROR</li>
<li><code>last_scanned</code>: Timestamp of last poll</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Stream Configuration</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Enabled</strong>: Yes</li>
<li><strong>View Type</strong>: NEW_AND_OLD_IMAGES</li>
<li><strong>Purpose</strong>: Triggers Step Function and Teams notification=
s</li>
</ul>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-RegressionTabl=
e:github-prs-regression-test-{env}">Regression Table: <code>github-prs-regr=
ession-test-{env}</code></h4>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Stores regression test PR data and accuracy me=
trics</p>
<p><strong>Key Structure</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Partition Key</strong>: <code>test_run_id</code> (String) - For=
mat: <code>test-run-{timestamp}</code></li>
<li><strong>Sort Key</strong>: <code>pr_id</code> (String) - Format: <code>=
{org}/{repo}#{pr_number}</code></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Key Attributes</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>test_run_id</code>: Unique test run identifier</li>
<li><code>pr_id</code>: PR identifier</li>
<li><code>repo_pr</code>: Repository and PR number</li>
<li><code>repository</code>: Repository name</li>
<li><code>pr_number</code>: PR number</li>
<li><code>execution_status</code>: RUNNING | COMPLETED | FAILED</li>
<li><code>security_status</code>: PASSED | FAILED | ERROR</li>
<li><code>compliance_status</code>: PASSED | FAILED | ERROR</li>
<li><code>iam_boundary_status</code>: PASSED | FAILED | ERROR</li>
<li><code>automated_decision</code>: PASSED | FAILED | ERROR</li>
<li><code>human_decision</code>: APPROVED | REJECTED</li>
<li><code>expected_result</code>: PASSED | FAILED</li>
<li><code>test_result</code>: MATCH | MISMATCH</li>
<li><code>timestamp</code>: Test execution timestamp</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Global Secondary Index</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Name</strong>: <code>repository-timestamp-index</code></li>
<li><strong>Partition Key</strong>: <code>repository</code></li>
<li><strong>Sort Key</strong>: <code>timestamp</code></li>
<li><strong>Purpose</strong>: Query test results by repository and time ran=
ge</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Stream Configuration</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Enabled</strong>: Yes</li>
<li><strong>View Type</strong>: NEW_AND_OLD_IMAGES</li>
<li><strong>Purpose</strong>: Triggers Step Function and aggregates results=
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-LambdaFunction=
s">Lambda Functions</h3>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-1.PRPollerLamb=
da">1. PR Poller Lambda</h4>
<p><strong>Function Name</strong>: <code>gts-github-pr-poll-poller-{env}</c=
ode><br><strong>Runtime</strong>: Python 3.12<br><strong>Timeout</strong>: =
300 seconds<br><strong>Memory</strong>: 512 MB<br><strong>VPC</strong>: Ena=
bled (for GitHub Enterprise access)</p>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Polls GitHub Enterprise for open PRs every 3 m=
inutes</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: EventBridge rule (rate: 3 minutes)</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Reads repository list from <code>config.json</code></li>
<li>Calls GitHub Enterprise API for each repository</li>
<li>Filters for open PRs</li>
<li>Inserts new PRs into DynamoDB (INSERT event)</li>
<li>Updates existing PRs with latest metadata (MODIFY event)</li>
<li>Detects <code>[REGRESSION-TEST]</code> tag for regression testing</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Environment Variables</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>DYNAMODB_TABLE</code>: Production table name</li>
<li><code>REGRESSION_DYNAMODB_TABLE</code>: Regression table name</li>
<li><code>HISTORICAL_S3_BUCKET</code>: S3 bucket for historical PR cache</l=
i>
<li><code>HISTORICAL_PR_FETCHER_FUNCTION</code>: Historical PR fetcher Lamb=
da name</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>IAM Permissions</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>DynamoDB: PutItem, UpdateItem on both tables</li>
<li>Secrets Manager: GetSecretValue (GitHub token)</li>
<li>Lambda: InvokeFunction (Historical PR Fetcher)</li>
<li>VPC: Network interface management</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-2.StepFunction=
TriggerLambda">2. Step Function Trigger Lambda</h4>
<p><strong>Function Name</strong>: <code>gts-github-pr-poll-stepfunction-tr=
igger-{env}</code><br><strong>Runtime</strong>: Python 3.12<br><strong>Time=
out</strong>: 60 seconds<br><strong>Memory</strong>: 256 MB</p>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Triggers Step Function workflow when new PR is=
 inserted</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: DynamoDB Stream (INSERT events only)</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Receives DynamoDB Stream event</li>
<li>Checks for idempotency (execution_id already exists)</li>
<li>Checks if final_status already exists (skip if present)</li>
<li>Normalizes event structure for regression tests</li>
<li>Starts appropriate Step Function execution</li>
<li>Updates DynamoDB with execution_id and execution_status=3DRUNNING</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Environment Variables</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>STEPFUNCTION_ARN</code>: Production Step Function ARN</li>
<li><code>REGRESSION_STEPFUNCTION_ARN</code>: Regression Step Function ARN<=
/li>
<li><code>DYNAMODB_TABLE</code>: Production table name</li>
<li><code>REGRESSION_DYNAMODB_TABLE</code>: Regression table name</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>IAM Permissions</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Step Functions: StartExecution</li>
<li>DynamoDB: UpdateItem on both tables</li>
<li>CloudWatch: PutLogEvents</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Event Source Mappings</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Production</strong>: Filters INSERT events from <code>github-op=
en-prs-{env}</code></li>
<li><strong>Regression</strong>: Filters INSERT events from <code>github-pr=
s-regression-test-{env}</code></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-3.SecurityScan=
LambdaDummy">3. Security Scan Lambda Dummy</h4>
<p><strong>Function Name</strong>: <code>gts-github-pr-poll-security-scan-{=
env}</code><br><strong>Runtime</strong>: Python 3.12<br><strong>Timeout</st=
rong>: 300 seconds<br><strong>Memory</strong>: 512 MB</p>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Validates IAM policy security requirements</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: Step Function (parallel execution)</p>
<p><strong>Validation Checks</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>IAM policy syntax validation dummy</li>
<li>Overly permissive permissions detection dummy</li>
<li>Wildcard usage in actions and resources dummy</li>
<li>Cross-account access validation dummy</li>
<li>Service control policy compliance dummy</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Input</strong>: DynamoDB event or regression test data</p>
<p><strong>Output</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "status": "PASSED" | "FAILED" | "ERROR",
  "details": "Detailed validation results"
}
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Environment Variables</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>ENVIRONMENT</code>: dev | prd</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-4.ComplianceCh=
eckLambdaDummy">4. Compliance Check Lambda Dummy</h4>
<p><strong>Function Name</strong>: <code>gts-github-pr-poll-compliance-chec=
k-{env}</code><br><strong>Runtime</strong>: Python 3.12<br><strong>Timeout<=
/strong>: 300 seconds<br><strong>Memory</strong>: 512 MB</p>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Validates IAM policy compliance requirements</=
p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: Step Function (parallel execution)</p>
<p><strong>Validation Checks</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Organizational policy compliance dummy</li>
<li>Required tags presence dummy</li>
<li>Naming convention adherence dummy</li>
<li>Resource limits compliance dummy</li>
<li>Audit logging requirements dummy</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Input</strong>: DynamoDB event or regression test data</p>
<p><strong>Output</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "status": "PASSED" | "FAILED" | "ERROR",
  "details": "Detailed validation results"
}
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Environment Variables</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>ENVIRONMENT</code>: dev | prd</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-5.IAMBoundaryC=
heckerLambda">5. IAM Boundary Checker Lambda</h4>
<p><strong>Function Name</strong>: <code>gts-github-pr-poll-iam-boundary-ch=
ecker-{env}</code><br><strong>Runtime</strong>: Python 3.12<br><strong>Time=
out</strong>: 300 seconds<br><strong>Memory</strong>: 512 MB<br><strong>VPC=
</strong>: Enabled (for GitHub Enterprise access)</p>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Validates IAM boundary policy requirements</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: Step Function (parallel execution)</p>
<p><strong>Validation Checks</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Boundary policy attachment verification</li>
<li>Boundary policy permissions validation</li>
<li>Effective permissions calculation</li>
<li>Boundary policy compliance with standards</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Input</strong>: DynamoDB event or regression test data</p>
<p><strong>Output</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "status": "PASSED" | "FAILED" | "ERROR",
  "details": "Detailed validation results"
}
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Environment Variables</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>GITHUB_API_BASE_URL</code>: GitHub Enterprise API URL</li>
<li><code>ENVIRONMENT</code>: dev | prd</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>IAM Permissions</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Secrets Manager: GetSecretValue (GitHub token)</li>
<li>VPC: Network interface management</li>
</ul>
