<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-7.FinalStatusC=
heckerLambda">7. Final Status Checker Lambda</h4>
<p><strong>Function Name</strong>: <code>gts-github-pr-poll-final-status-ch=
ecker-{env}</code><br><strong>Runtime</strong>: Python 3.12<br><strong>Time=
out</strong>: 60 seconds<br><strong>Memory</strong>: 256 MB</p>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Determines overall PASS/FAIL/ERROR status</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: Step Function (after parallel checks complete)=
</p>
<p><strong>Logic</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-python">if all checks PASSED:
    final_status =3D "PASSED"
elif any check ERROR:
    final_status =3D "ERROR"
else:
    final_status =3D "FAILED"
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Reads validation results from DynamoDB</li>
<li>Applies decision logic</li>
<li>Updates DynamoDB with final_status</li>
<li>For regression tests: Compares with human_decision (logic not implement=
ed yet)</li>
<li>Invokes Regression Summary Lambda (if regression test)</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Environment Variables</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>DYNAMODB_TABLE</code>: Production table name</li>
<li><code>REGRESSION_DYNAMODB_TABLE</code>: Regression table name</li>
<li><code>REGRESSION_SUMMARY_FUNCTION</code>: Regression Summary Lambda nam=
e</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>IAM Permissions</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>DynamoDB: GetItem, UpdateItem on both tables</li>
<li>Lambda: InvokeFunction (Regression Summary)</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-8.TeamsNotifie=
rLambda">8. Teams Notifier Lambda</h4>
<p><strong>Function Name</strong>: <code>gts-github-pr-poll-notifier-{env}<=
/code><br><strong>Runtime</strong>: Python 3.12<br><strong>Timeout</strong>=
: 60 seconds<br><strong>Memory</strong>: 256 MB</p>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Sends notifications to MS Teams channels</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: DynamoDB Stream (MODIFY events where execution=
_status=3DCOMPLETED)</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Receives DynamoDB Stream event</li>
<li>Validates execution_status changed to COMPLETED</li>
<li>Validates final_status exists</li>
<li>Determines routing based on repository and test_run_id</li>
<li>Builds Teams adaptive card</li>
<li>Sends notification to appropriate channel</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Channel Routing Logic</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-python">if test_run_id exists:
    channel =3D "IAM-PR-Automation-Regression"
elif "github-pr-poll-poc" in repo_pr:
    channel =3D "IAM-PR-Automation-Test"
else:
    channel =3D "IAM-PR-Automation"
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Environment Variables</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>TEAMS_WEBHOOK_URL</code>: Production channel webhook</li>
<li><code>TEAMS_REGRESSION_WEBHOOK_URL</code>: Regression channel webhook</=
li>
<li><code>ENVIRONMENT</code>: dev | prd</li>
<li><code>GITHUB_PR_TABLE</code>: Production table name</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>IAM Permissions</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>DynamoDB: GetItem (for additional PR details)</li>
<li>Secrets Manager: GetSecretValue (Teams webhooks)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Event Source Mapping</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Filter</strong>: MODIFY events where <code>execution_status =3D=
 "COMPLETED"</code></li>
<li><strong>Batch Size</strong>: 1</li>
<li><strong>Starting Position</strong>: LATEST</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-9.HistoricalPR=
FetcherLambda">9. Historical PR Fetcher Lambda</h4>
<p><strong>Function Name</strong>: <code>gts-github-pr-poll-historical-pr-f=
etcher-{env}</code><br><strong>Runtime</strong>: Python 3.12<br><strong>Tim=
eout</strong>: 900 seconds (15 minutes)<br><strong>Memory</strong>: 1024 MB=
<br><strong>VPC</strong>: Enabled (for GitHub Enterprise access)</p>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Fetches historical PRs for regression testing<=
/p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: Manual invocation or PR Poller (for regression=
 tests)</p>
<p><strong>Operation Modes</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>incremental_update</strong>: Fetches and caches historical PRs =
to S3</li>
<li><strong>regression_test</strong>: Loads cached PRs and inserts into reg=
ression table</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Sampling Parameters</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>max_prs</code>: Maximum PRs to fetch (default: unlimited)</li>
<li><code>decision_filter</code>: APPROVED | REJECTED | ALL</li>
<li><code>random_seed</code>: Seed for reproducible sampling</li>
<li><code>repositories</code>: List of repositories to sample from</li>
<li><code>per_repo_limit</code>: Maximum PRs per repository</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Process (incremental_update)</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Fetches closed PRs from GitHub Enterprise</li>
<li>Parses PR metadata and human decision</li>
<li>Caches to S3 (organized by repo/year/month)</li>
<li>Returns cache summary</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Process (regression_test)</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Loads cached PRs from S3</li>
<li>Applies sampling strategy</li>
<li>Inserts selected PRs into regression table</li>
<li>Returns test run summary</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Environment Variables</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>HISTORICAL_S3_BUCKET</code>: S3 bucket for PR cache</li>
<li><code>REGRESSION_DYNAMODB_TABLE</code>: Regression table name</li>
<li><code>GITHUB_API_BASE_URL</code>: GitHub Enterprise API URL</li>
<li><code>ENVIRONMENT</code>: dev | prd</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>IAM Permissions</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>S3: GetObject, PutObject on historical bucket</li>
<li>DynamoDB: PutItem on regression table</li>
<li>Secrets Manager: GetSecretValue (GitHub token)</li>
<li>VPC: Network interface management</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-10.RegressionS=
ummaryLambda">10. Regression Summary Lambda</h4>
<p><strong>Function Name</strong>: <code>gts-github-pr-poll-regression-summ=
ary-{env}</code><br><strong>Runtime</strong>: Python 3.12<br><strong>Timeou=
t</strong>: 60 seconds<br><strong>Memory</strong>: 256 MB</p>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Aggregates regression test results and calcula=
tes accuracy</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: Final Status Checker Lambda (for regression te=
sts)</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Queries all results for test_run_id</li>
<li>Calculates accuracy metrics:=20
<ul>
<li>Total PRs tested</li>
<li>MATCH count (automation agrees with human)</li>
<li>MISMATCH count (automation disagrees with human)</li>
<li>Accuracy percentage</li>
<li>False positive rate</li>
<li>False negative rate</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Sends summary to Teams regression channel</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Metrics Calculated</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-python">accuracy =3D (MATCH_count / total_PRs)=
 * 100
false_positive_rate =3D (PASSED_but_REJECTED / total_REJECTED) * 100
false_negative_rate =3D (FAILED_but_APPROVED / total_APPROVED) * 100
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Environment Variables</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>REGRESSION_DYNAMODB_TABLE</code>: Regression table name</li>
<li><code>TEAMS_REGRESSION_WEBHOOK_URL</code>: Regression channel webhook</=
li>
<li><code>ENVIRONMENT</code>: dev | prd</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>IAM Permissions</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>DynamoDB: Query on regression table</li>
<li>Secrets Manager: GetSecretValue (Teams webhook)</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-StepFunctions"=
>Step Functions</h3>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Production/Tes=
tStepFunction">Production/Test Step Function</h4>
<p><strong>Name</strong>: <code>gts-github-pr-poll-iam-pr-workflow-{env}</c=
ode><br><strong>Definition File</strong>: <code>definition-{env}.json</code=
> (dev or prd)</p>
<p><strong>States</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>SetExecutionRunning</strong>: Updates execution_status to RUNNI=
NG</li>
<li><strong>ParallelChecks</strong>: Runs three validation checks in parall=
el=20
<ul>
<li>SecurityScanStep =E2=86=92 UpdateSecurityScanResult</li>
<li>ComplianceCheckStep =E2=86=92 UpdateComplianceCheckResult</li>
<li>IAMBoundaryCheckStep =E2=86=92 UpdateIAMBoundaryCheckResult</li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong>SetFinalStatus</strong>: Invokes Final Status Checker Lambda</l=
i>
<li><strong>WorkflowComplete</strong>: Updates execution_status to COMPLETE=
D</li>
<li><strong>WorkflowSuccess</strong>: Terminal success state</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Error Handling</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Retry logic on all Lambda invocations (3 attempts, exponential backoff)=
</li>
<li>Catch blocks update DynamoDB with ERROR status</li>
<li>SetExecutionFailed state for catastrophic failures</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Input</strong>: DynamoDB Stream event from production table</p>
<p><strong>Output</strong>: Updated DynamoDB record with all validation res=
ults</p>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-RegressionStep=
Function">Regression Step Function</h4>
<p><strong>Name</strong>: <code>gts-github-pr-poll-iam-pr-regression-workfl=
ow-{env}</code><br><strong>Definition File</strong>: <code>definition-regre=
ssion.json</code></p>
<p><strong>Key Differences from Production</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Uses composite key (test_run_id + pr_id)</li>
<li>Accepts pr_data from S3 cache (not DynamoDB stream)</li>
<li>Sets regression_mode flag for Lambda functions</li>
<li>Uses different field names (security_status vs security_scan_endstatus)=
</li>
<li>Updates automated_decision instead of final_status</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>States</strong>: Same structure as production workflow</p>
<p><strong>Input</strong>: Regression test data with pr_data from S3</p>
<p><strong>Output</strong>: Updated regression table record with test resul=
ts</p>
<hr>
