<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-ProductionWork=
flowSteps">Production Workflow Steps</h3>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step1:PRCreati=
on(T+0)">Step 1: PR Creation (T+0)</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: Developer creates PR in GitHub Enterprise</p>
<p><strong>Example</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Repository: <code>Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod</code></l=
i>
<li>PR Number: 250</li>
<li>Title: "GTBT-7000: Add new IAM role for data analytics"</li>
<li>Author: jsmith</li>
<li>Status: OPEN</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>DynamoDB State</strong>: None (PR not detected yet)</p>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step2:PRDetect=
ion(T+0toT+180seconds)">Step 2: PR Detection (T+0 to T+180 seconds)</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: PR Poller Lambda discovers new PR</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: EventBridge rule (every 3 minutes)</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>EventBridge invokes PR Poller Lambda</li>
<li>Lambda polls GitHub Enterprise API for each repository</li>
<li>Discovers PR #250 (status: OPEN)</li>
<li>Inserts new record into DynamoDB</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>DynamoDB INSERT</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "repo_pr": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod#250",
  "repo": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod",
  "pr_number": 250,
  "title": "GTBT-7000: Add new IAM role for data analytics",
  "author": "jsmith",
  "created_at": "2025-11-25T10:00:00Z",
  "updated_at": "2025-11-25T10:00:00Z",
  "last_scanned": "2025-11-25T10:02:30Z",
  "url": "https://git.us.aegon.com/Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-p=
rod/pull/250"
}
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Important</strong>: INSERT event does NOT trigger Teams Notifier=
 (filter requires MODIFY with execution_status=3DCOMPLETED)</p>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step3:Workflow=
Trigger(T+2-3seconds)">Step 3: Workflow Trigger (T+2-3 seconds)</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: DynamoDB Stream triggers Step Function</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: DynamoDB Stream INSERT event</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Stream event delivered to Step Function Trigger Lambda</li>
<li>Lambda checks idempotency (execution_id not present)</li>
<li>Lambda checks if already processed (final_status not present)</li>
<li>Lambda starts Step Function execution</li>
<li>Lambda updates DynamoDB with execution metadata</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>DynamoDB UPDATE</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "repo_pr": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod#250",
  "execution_id": "abc123-def456-ghi789",
  "execution_status": "RUNNING",
  "execution_timestamp": "2025-11-25T10:02:33Z"
}
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Important</strong>: This UPDATE creates MODIFY event, but Teams =
Notifier does NOT trigger (execution_status=3DRUNNING, not COMPLETED)</p>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step4:SetExecu=
tionRunning(T+3seconds)">Step 4: Set Execution Running (T+3 seconds)</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: Step Function updates execution status</p>
<p><strong>State</strong>: SetExecutionRunning</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Step Function reads repo_pr from input</li>
<li>Updates DynamoDB with execution_status=3DRUNNING</li>
<li>Preserves original input for downstream states (ResultPath)</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>DynamoDB UPDATE</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "execution_status": "RUNNING",
  "execution_timestamp": "2025-11-25T10:02:33Z"
}
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Important</strong>: This UPDATE creates MODIFY event, but Teams =
Notifier does NOT trigger (execution_status=3DRUNNING)</p>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step5:Parallel=
Validation(T+4toT+8seconds)">Step 5: Parallel Validation (T+4 to T+8 second=
s)</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: Three validation checks run in parallel</p>
<p><strong>State</strong>: ParallelChecks</p>
<p><strong>Branch 1: Security Scan</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Invokes Security Scan Lambda</li>
<li>Validates IAM policy security</li>
<li>Returns: <code>{status: "PASSED", details: {...}}</code></li>
<li>Updates DynamoDB: <code>security_scan_endstatus =3D "PASSED"</code></li=
>
</ul>
<p><strong>Branch 2: Compliance Check</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Invokes Compliance Check Lambda</li>
<li>Validates IAM policy compliance</li>
<li>Returns: <code>{status: "PASSED", details: {...}}</code></li>
<li>Updates DynamoDB: <code>compliance_check_endstatus =3D "PASSED"</code><=
/li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Branch 3: IAM Boundary Check</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Invokes IAM Boundary Checker Lambda</li>
<li>Validates boundary policies</li>
<li>Returns: <code>{status: "PASSED", details: {...}}</code></li>
<li>Updates DynamoDB: <code>iam_boundary_check_endstatus =3D "PASSED"</code=
></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>DynamoDB State After Parallel Checks</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "repo_pr": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod#250",
  "execution_status": "RUNNING",
  "security_scan_endstatus": "PASSED",
  "compliance_check_endstatus": "PASSED",
  "iam_boundary_check_endstatus": "PASSED"
}
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Important</strong>: These UPDATEs create MODIFY events, but Team=
s Notifier does NOT trigger (execution_status=3DRUNNING)</p>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step6:FinalSta=
tusDetermination(T+9seconds)">Step 6: Final Status Determination (T+9 secon=
ds)</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: Final Status Checker determines overall result<=
/p>
<p><strong>State</strong>: SetFinalStatus</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Step Function invokes Final Status Checker Lambda</li>
<li>Lambda reads validation results from DynamoDB</li>
<li>Lambda applies decision logic:<pre><code class=3D"language-python">if a=
ll checks PASSED:
    final_status =3D "PASSED"
elif any check ERROR:
    final_status =3D "ERROR"
else:
    final_status =3D "FAILED"
</code></pre></li>
<li>Lambda updates DynamoDB with final_status</li>
<li>Lambda returns result to Step Function</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>DynamoDB UPDATE</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "final_status": "PASSED"
}
</code></pre>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step7:Workflow=
Complete(T+10seconds)">Step 7: Workflow Complete (T+10 seconds)</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: Step Function marks execution complete</p>
<p><strong>State</strong>: WorkflowComplete</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Step Function updates DynamoDB</li>
<li>Sets execution_status =3D "COMPLETED"</li>
<li>Transitions to WorkflowSuccess state</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>DynamoDB UPDATE (FINAL)</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "repo_pr": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod#250",
  "title": "GTBT-7000: Add new IAM role for data analytics",
  "author": "jsmith",
  "execution_id": "abc123-def456-ghi789",
  "execution_status": "COMPLETED",
  "execution_timestamp": "2025-11-25T10:02:33Z",
  "security_scan_endstatus": "PASSED",
  "compliance_check_endstatus": "PASSED",
  "iam_boundary_check_endstatus": "PASSED",
  "final_status": "PASSED",
  "last_scanned": "2025-11-25T10:02:30Z"
}
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Important</strong>: This UPDATE creates MODIFY event where:</p>
<ul>
<li>OldImage.execution_status =3D "RUNNING"</li>
<li>NewImage.execution_status =3D "COMPLETED"</li>
<li>NewImage.final_status =3D "PASSED"</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Teams Notifier Trigger</strong>: =E2=9C=85 YES</p>
<ul>
<li>Filter matches: eventName=3DMODIFY AND execution_status=3DCOMPLETED</li=
>
<li>Lambda validates: execution_status changed to COMPLETED</li>
<li>Lambda validates: final_status exists</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step8:TeamsNot=
ification(T+11seconds)">Step 8: Teams Notification (T+11 seconds)</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: Teams Notifier sends notification</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: DynamoDB Stream MODIFY event</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Stream event delivered to Teams Notifier Lambda</li>
<li>Lambda validates execution_status changed to COMPLETED</li>
<li>Lambda validates final_status exists</li>
<li>Lambda determines routing:=20
<ul>
<li>No test_run_id =E2=86=92 Not regression test</li>
<li>Repository =3D "idc-gts-roles-prod" =E2=86=92 Production channel</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Lambda builds Teams adaptive card</li>
<li>Lambda sends notification</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Teams Channel</strong>: IAM-PR-Automation (production)</p>
<p><strong>Notification Content</strong>:</p>
<pre><code>=E2=9C=85 PR #250 - All Checks Passed

Repository: Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod
Author: jsmith
Title: GTBT-7000: Add new IAM role for data analytics

Validation Results:
=E2=9C=85 Security Scan: PASSED
=E2=9C=85 Compliance Check: PASSED
=E2=9C=85 IAM Boundary Check: PASSED

Overall Status: =E2=9C=85 PASSED

[View PR](https://git.us.aegon.com/Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-p=
rod/pull/250)
</code></pre>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-ProductionWork=
flowSummary">Production Workflow Summary</h3>
<p><strong>Total Duration</strong>: ~10-15 seconds (after PR detection)</p>
<p><strong>Key Points</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>PR detection happens within 3 minutes (polling interval)</li>
<li>Validation checks run in parallel for speed</li>
<li>Teams notification sent only when execution completes</li>
<li>Loop prevention via event filters and idempotency checks</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Possible Outcomes</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>=E2=9C=85 <strong>PASSED</strong>: All validation checks passed</li>
<li>=E2=9D=8C <strong>FAILED</strong>: One or more validation checks failed=
</li>
<li>=E2=9A=A0=EF=B8=8F <strong>ERROR</strong>: System error during validati=
on</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-TestWorkflow">=
Test Workflow</h2>
<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Overview.2">Ov=
erview</h3>
<p>The test workflow validates PRs from the POC repository (<code>CSET/gith=
ub-pr-poll-poc</code>). It follows the same process as production but route=
s notifications to a different Teams channel.</p>
<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-KeyDifferences=
fromProduction">Key Differences from Production</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
