<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-TestWorkflowSt=
eps">Test Workflow Steps</h3>
<p>Steps 1-7 are identical to production workflow.</p>
<p><strong>Step 8: Teams Notification (Different Channel)</strong></p>
<p><strong>Routing Logic</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-python">if "github-pr-poll-poc" in repo_pr:
    channel =3D "IAM-PR-Automation-Test"
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Teams Channel</strong>: IAM-PR-Automation-Test</p>
<p><strong>Typical Notification</strong> (POC repo has no IAM policies):</p=
>
<pre><code>=E2=9D=8C PR #22 - Checks Failed

Repository: CSET/github-pr-poll-poc
Author: asmith10
Title: Test: Loop Fix Validation

