<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-RegressionTest=
ingWorkflowSteps">Regression Testing Workflow Steps</h3>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step1:TestInit=
iation(T+0)">Step 1: Test Initiation (T+0)</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: Trigger historical PR data collection</p>
<p><strong>Methods</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Manual Lambda Invocation</strong>: Direct AWS Lambda invoke</li=
>
<li><strong>PR-Triggered</strong>: Create PR with <code>[REGRESSION-TEST]</=
code> tag in POC repo</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Historical PR Fetcher Lambda invoked</li>
<li>Mode: <code>incremental_update</code></li>
<li>Fetches closed PRs from GitHub Enterprise</li>
<li>Caches PR data to S3</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>S3 Cache Structure</strong>:</p>
<pre><code>s3://iam-automation-historical-prs-dev/
=E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 Centralized-IAM-Accounts/
    =E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 idc-gts-roles-prod/
        =E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 2025/
            =E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 10/
                =E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=94=80 pr-180.json
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Cached PR Data</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "pr_id": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod#180",
  "repository": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod",
  "pr_number": 180,
  "title": "GTBT-6500: Update IAM role permissions",
  "author": "jdoe",
  "created_at": "2025-10-10T12:00:00Z",
  "closed_at": "2025-10-15T10:30:00Z",
  "state": "closed",
  "merged": true,
  "human_decision": "APPROVED",
  "decision_timestamp": "2025-10-15T10:30:00Z",
  "cached_at": "2025-11-25T14:30:00Z"
}
</code></pre>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step2:Regressi=
onTestTrigger(T+1second)">Step 2: Regression Test Trigger (T+1 second)</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: Load cached PRs and insert into regression tabl=
e</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Historical PR Fetcher Lambda invoked again</li>
<li>Mode: <code>regression_test</code></li>
<li>Loads cached PRs from S3</li>
<li>Applies sampling strategy (if configured)</li>
<li>Inserts selected PRs into regression table</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Sampling Parameters</strong> (optional):</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "max_prs": 50,
  "decision_filter": "ALL",
  "random_seed": 12345,
  "repositories": null,
  "per_repo_limit": null
}
</code></pre>
<p><strong>DynamoDB INSERT</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "test_run_id": "test-run-2025-11-25-001",
  "pr_id": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod#180",
  "repo_pr": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod#180",
  "repo": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod",
  "pr_number": 180,
  "title": "GTBT-6500: Update IAM role permissions",
  "author": "jdoe",
  "human_decision": "APPROVED",
  "expected_result": "PASSED",
  "test_timestamp": "2025-11-25T14:30:00Z"
}
</code></pre>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step3:Workflow=
Trigger(T+2seconds)">Step 3: Workflow Trigger (T+2 seconds)</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: DynamoDB Stream triggers Step Function</p>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: DynamoDB Stream INSERT event (regression table=
)</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Stream event delivered to Step Function Trigger Lambda</li>
<li>Lambda detects regression test (test_run_id present)</li>
<li>Lambda normalizes event structure</li>
<li>Lambda starts Regression Step Function execution</li>
<li>Lambda updates DynamoDB with execution metadata</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>DynamoDB UPDATE</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "test_run_id": "test-run-2025-11-25-001",
  "pr_id": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod#180",
  "execution_id": "xyz789-abc123-def456",
  "execution_status": "RUNNING",
  "execution_timestamp": "2025-11-25T14:30:02Z"
}
</code></pre>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Steps4-7:Valid=
ationExecution">Steps 4-7: Validation Execution</h4>
<p><strong>Process</strong>: Same as production workflow, but with regressi=
on-specific differences</p>
<p><strong>Key Differences</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Uses <code>github-prs-regression-test-{env}</code> table</li>
<li>Uses composite key (test_run_id + pr_id)</li>
<li>Field names differ:=20
<ul>
<li><code>security_status</code> (not security_scan_endstatus)</li>
<li><code>compliance_status</code> (not compliance_check_endstatus)</li>
<li><code>iam_boundary_status</code> (not iam_boundary_check_endstatus)</li=
>
<li><code>automated_decision</code> (not final_status)</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Lambda functions receive <code>regression_mode: true</code> flag</li>
<li>PR data comes from S3 cache (not live GitHub API)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>DynamoDB State After Validation</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "test_run_id": "test-run-2025-11-25-001",
  "pr_id": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod#180",
  "execution_status": "COMPLETED",
  "security_status": "PASSED",
  "compliance_status": "PASSED",
  "iam_boundary_status": "PASSED",
  "automated_decision": "PASSED",
  "human_decision": "APPROVED",
  "expected_result": "PASSED"
}
</code></pre>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step8:ResultsC=
omparisonandAggregation">Step 8: Results Comparison and Aggregation</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: Compare automation decision with human decision=
</p>
<p><strong>Process</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Final Status Checker Lambda compares results:<pre><code class=3D"langua=
ge-python">if automated_decision =3D=3D expected_result:
    test_result =3D "MATCH"
else:
    test_result =3D "MISMATCH"
</code></pre></li>
<li>Lambda updates DynamoDB with test_result</li>
<li>Lambda invokes Regression Summary Lambda</li>
<li>Regression Summary aggregates all results for test_run_id</li>
<li>Regression Summary calculates accuracy metrics</li>
<li>Regression Summary sends notification to Teams</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>DynamoDB FINAL UPDATE</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-json">{
  "test_run_id": "test-run-2025-11-25-001",
  "pr_id": "Centralized-IAM-Accounts/idc-gts-roles-prod#180",
  "execution_status": "COMPLETED",
  "automated_decision": "PASSED",
  "human_decision": "APPROVED",
  "expected_result": "PASSED",
  "test_result": "MATCH"
}
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Accuracy Metrics</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-python">total_prs =3D 50
match_count =3D 45
mismatch_count =3D 5

accuracy =3D (match_count / total_prs) * 100  # 90%

# False Positive: Automation PASSED but human REJECTED
false_positive_count =3D 2
false_positive_rate =3D (2 / total_rejected) * 100  # 4%

# False Negative: Automation FAILED but human APPROVED
false_negative_count =3D 3
false_negative_rate =3D (3 / total_approved) * 100  # 6%
</code></pre>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-Step9:TeamsNot=
ification">Step 9: Teams Notification</h4>
<p><strong>Action</strong>: Teams Notifier sends regression test summary</p=
>
<p><strong>Trigger</strong>: DynamoDB Stream MODIFY event (execution_status=
=3DCOMPLETED)</p>
<p><strong>Routing Logic</strong>:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-python">if test_run_id exists:
    channel =3D "IAM-PR-Automation-Regression"
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Teams Channel</strong>: IAM-PR-Automation-Regression</p>
<p><strong>Notification Content</strong> (MATCH):</p>
<pre><code>=E2=9C=85 Regression Test - MATCH

