<hr>
<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-RegressionTest=
ingSummary">Regression Testing Summary</h3>
<p><strong>Total Duration</strong>: ~20-30 minutes (full test cycle with 50=
 PRs)</p>
<p><strong>Key Points</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Uses historical PR data from S3 cache</li>
<li>Compares automation decisions with human decisions</li>
<li>Measures accuracy, false positive rate, false negative rate</li>
<li>Separate DynamoDB table with composite key</li>
<li>Different Step Function definition (regression mode)</li>
<li>Aggregated summary sent to Teams</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Possible Test Results</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>=E2=9C=85 <strong>MATCH</strong>: Automation agrees with human decision=
</li>
<li>=E2=9A=A0=EF=B8=8F <strong>MISMATCH</strong>: Automation disagrees with=
 human decision (needs tuning)</li>
</ul>
