<h2 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-MonitoringandN=
otifications">Monitoring and Notifications</h2>
<h3 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-MSTeamsChannel=
s">MS Teams Channels</h3>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-1.IAM-PR-Autom=
ation(Production)">1. IAM-PR-Automation (Production)</h4>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Production PR notifications</p>
<p><strong>Receives</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>PRs from IDC repositories (idc-*-roles-prod)</li>
<li>Real-time validation results</li>
<li>PASSED/FAILED/ERROR status</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Notification Frequency</strong>: Per PR (within 15-20 seconds of=
 completion)</p>
<p><strong>Typical Messages</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>=E2=9C=85 "PR #250 - All Checks Passed"</li>
<li>=E2=9D=8C "PR #251 - Checks Failed"</li>
<li>=E2=9A=A0=EF=B8=8F "PR #252 - Error During Validation"</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-2.IAM-PR-Autom=
ation-Test(Test)">2. IAM-PR-Automation-Test (Test)</h4>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Test PR notifications from POC repository</p>
<p><strong>Receives</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>PRs from CSET/github-pr-poll-poc</li>
<li>Test validation results</li>
<li>Usually FAILED (no IAM policies in test repo)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Notification Frequency</strong>: Per PR (within 15-20 seconds of=
 completion)</p>
<p><strong>Typical Messages</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>=E2=9D=8C "PR #22 - Checks Failed (No IAM policy files found)"</li>
<li>=E2=9C=85 "PR #23 - All Checks Passed" (if test IAM policies added)</li=
>
</ul>
