<h4 id=3D"IAMPRAutomationWorkflowCompleteSystemDocumentation-3.IAM-PR-Autom=
ation-Regression(Regression)">3. IAM-PR-Automation-Regression (Regression)<=
/h4>
<p><strong>Purpose</strong>: Regression test results and accuracy metrics</=
p>
<p><strong>Receives</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Individual regression test results (MATCH/MISMATCH)</li>
<li>Aggregated test summaries</li>
<li>Accuracy metrics and trends</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Notification Frequency</strong>:</p>
<ul>
