ctices">Logging Best Practices</h3>
<p><strong>Log Levels</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>INFO</strong>: Normal operations, PR discoveries, validation re=
sults</li>
<li><strong>WARNING</strong>: Retries, temporary failures, missing data</li=
>
<li><strong>ERROR</strong>: Validation failures, API errors, system errors<=
/li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Key Log Events</strong>:</p>
<ul>
